## Shipping your tickets

As soon as you have your tickets and are ready to ship them to your buyer, use
the [`sale:shipments`](#saleshipments) link to get the [`Shipments`](#shipments)
resource related to your sale. When you are ready to ship, follow the
[`shipment:create`](#shipmentcreate) create a [`Shipment`](#shipment) and then
follow the [`shipment:label`](#shipmentlabel) link to get the full details on
how to ship the tickets.
